Key Match Events: Rohit Sharma scored an unbeaten 117 while Shami took 7 wickets for 57 runs
Mitchell and Williamson shared a crucial partnership of 134 runs
Shami dismissed Daryl Mitchell and Santner in the final overs
India won by 70 runs to secure their place in the final
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma praised the team's composure despite pressure and mentioned the importance of staying calm
Mohammed Shami reflected on his performance and mentioned the importance of staying focused
New Zealand's captain Kane Williamson and Mitchell's performances were acknowledged
Miscellaneous Highlights: India will face the winner of the Australia vs South Africa match in the final
India's victory secured their place in the final of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023
